description:
Kult has achieved legendary status among roleplaying gamers. Melding gnostic and kabbalistic lore with a contemporary-horror approach, the story of humanity's escape from an illusion masking a hellish reality is a one-of-a-kind experience.

The Kult series introduces this setting anew with parole officer Tomas Zenk, one of the few who can pierce the illusion. As he overcomes monsters sent to kill him, Zenk discovers the true extent of his powers, including the ability to exert control over the machinery of humanity's enslavement. But will he aid the forces attempting to bring down the illusion . . . or succumb to the temptations of power?

The legendary RPG comes to comics!
name: Kult Part One Of Four

description: Dee and Kelly decided, with the usual , unknowing, complicity of Angie, to make a mysterious plan of Nikola Tesla, who could assure them , as the two shabby criminals hope , the world domination .
name: La ragazza nella torta

description: A mysterious epidemic of "truth" has spread from Ohio , reaching even the Altrove secret base. Martin must discover the cause , before too much truth destroys the world itself .
name: La macchina della verità

description: This same cover was used five years earlier in the same series.

A young and ignorant peasant tries to blackmail the U.S. with the help of a pendulum, created by John Dee, able to accurately predict the weather. Dee and Kelly, looking for Angie, have a similar one, but do not know how to use it . Altrove attempts to neutralize the blackmail conspiring against the weather. And Martin, like every summer, is in the middle.
name: Il mago della pioggia
